<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2601538>
    dc:description "FIGURES 60–62. Halozercon kazachok sp. n., 60. Deutonymph, ventral idiosoma. 61. Protonymph, dorsal idiosoma; 62. Protonymph, ventral idiosoma." ;
